{
  "stem": "18654.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I put my handbag on top of my suitcase at the bus stop with my 15-- with about 15 shillings in it, which I had saved.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I turned around to pick it up, it had disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why I remember it so clearly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I lost my-- my worldly possessions, practically.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she must have taken me to this home-- I can't remember-- or hostel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There I was a very unhappy at first, because it was a very big change from the children's home to this girls' hostel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were kept-- in-- in Cornwall we were treated like little children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to be in bed by half past 7:00.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to go out on our own.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And suddenly I came back to London.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was terrified.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was traffic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wasn't used to traffic to start with.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was very frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And suddenly I was-- seemed to be more-- I had to be responsible for myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We weren't treated like children there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had to be home by a certain time in the evenings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had to, of course, behave ourselves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We always had to home Friday nights, because of the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I remember, we usually went to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Again, being a B'nai B'rith hostel, it was kosher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it was run by a Miss [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Falk. ?] And I was very unhappy there at first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I remember phoning my committee, and saying, if you don't get me out of here, I'm going to run away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I had no intentions of really running away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because I didn't know where to run to, and I had no money, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I was still at school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I wasn't earning any money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By this time I wasn't going to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
